                        future, by assisting them to find their new academic prowess with simplicity, an easy
                        step-by-step
                        process, and to take off that stress off their shoulders.</p>
                    <br>
                    {%if current_user.is_authenticated%}
                    <div class="d-grid gap-2 d-sm-flex justify-content-sm-center">
                        <a href="/settings"><button type="button"
                                class="btn btn-outline-warning btn-lg px-4 gap-3">Continue</button></a>
                        {%else%}
                        <a href="#sign_up"><button type="button" class="btn btn-outline-warning btn-lg px-3 gap-5">Sign
                                Up</button></a>
                        <a href="/sign_in"><button type="button" class="btn btn-outline-warning btn-lg px-3 gap-5">Sign
                                In</button></a>
                    </div>
